
# ğŸ“˜ Smart Course Recommendation System

An **intelligent course recommendation system** built with **Java, JDBC, MySQL, and Data Structures**.
It suggests courses to students based on their completed courses and prerequisites using **graph traversal algorithms (BFS/DFS)**.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

* ğŸ”‘ **User Authentication** â€“ Student/Admin login.
* ğŸ“š **Course Management** â€“ Add, view, and manage courses.
* ğŸ¯ **Recommendation Engine** â€“ Suggests next courses using graph algorithms.
* âš¡ **Data Structures Used:**

  * Graph (Adjacency List) â†’ Course prerequisites
  * Queue & Stack â†’ BFS/DFS traversals
  * HashMap â†’ Fast course lookup
  * PriorityQueue â†’ Ranking courses by difficulty/popularity
* ğŸ—„ **Database Integration (MySQL)** â€“ Users, courses, enrollments, prerequisites.

---

## ğŸ›  Tech Stack

* **Programming Language:** Java
* **Database:** MySQL
* **Libraries/Tools:** JDBC, Scanner (Java Console I/O)
* **Data Structures:** Graph, Queue, Stack, HashMap, PriorityQueue

