## âš™ï¸ Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/SmartCourseRecommendationSystem.git
cd SmartCourseRecommendationSystem
```

### 2. Import Database

1. Open MySQL.
2. Run the schema file:

   ```bash
   mysql -u root -p course_recommendation < sql/schema.sql
   ```

### 3. Configure Database Connection

Update your DB credentials in:
`src/db/DBConnection.java`

```java
private static final String URL = "jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/course_recommendation";
private static final String USER = "root";   // change if needed
private static final String PASSWORD = "root"; // change if needed
```

### 4. Compile & Run

```bash
javac -d bin src/**/*.java
java -cp bin Main
```

